@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_omulgm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.75) * 0.57) * (wp.sin(v1 + 0.37) / (tmp + 0.50 + v2 + 0.20)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp((v2 + 0.70 * tmp + 0.84)))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
